&lt;p>Il me manquait la recherche sur Hugo, &lt;em>j&amp;rsquo;en est chié&lt;/em> une histoire de Jquery.&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="configtoml">config.toml&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>On va demander a Hugo de générer un fichier JSON, pour récupérer les données du site.&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code class="language-toml" data-lang="toml">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>[&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e">outputs&lt;/span>]
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e">home&lt;/span> = [ &lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#34;HTML&amp;#34;&lt;/span>, &lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#34;JSON&amp;#34;&lt;/span>, &lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#34;RSS&amp;#34;&lt;/span>]&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>
&lt;p>Quand on lance Hugo, on a droit a une erreur.&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>Change of config file detected, rebuilding site.
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>2023-05-02 11:39:09.348 +0200
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>WARN 2023/05/02 11:39:09 found no layout file &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef">for&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#34;JSON&amp;#34;&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef">for&lt;/span> kind &lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#34;home&amp;#34;&lt;/span>: You should create a template file which matches Hugo Layouts Lookup Rules &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef">for&lt;/span> this combination.
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>Rebuilt in &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff">205&lt;/span> ms&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>
&lt;h2 id="indexjson">Index.json&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>il faut créer le fichier &lt;em>index.json&lt;/em> dans notre theme &lt;em>themes/schrek/layouts&lt;/em>&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>